Full Description: Tradingsim is the first trading simulator that works directly over the internet browser and does not require any downloads.  Tradingsim is for anyone interested in active trading.  This could range from a seasoned hedge fund manager, to your stay-at-home mom.  Users can practice trading Nasdaq stocks 24-hours a day using real historical tick data.  Tradingsim provides data on over 5,000 Nasdaq symbols.  This means that users interested in learning to trade the heavy hitters like Apple, Google, or Intel, can now do so without having to sign-up for a brokerage.   Tradingsim has pause, play and fast forward controls which allow a trader to further dissect the market to identify strategies that best fit their trading style.  Tradingsim is taking the lead on providing visibility into the often "mystical" world of active trading.  Through the use of their free web-based platform, Tradingsim hopes to educate investors around the world on how to make money actively trading stocks.
